            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the Greek cheese is cooking, wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the<strong> wilted spinach</strong> under <strong>cold running water </strong>until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can then roughly chop</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678375679182-x200.jpg",
