          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the couscous is done, add the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> and <strong>chopped dates</strong> to the cooked couscous and mix it all together – this is your <strong>spiced couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
